 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the french##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the person watching zombie movies and the blend-smoker##2
 7. the chaman-smoker is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the french##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the blend-smoker##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the polish##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
