 8. the canadian is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is handball is the person driving the bike##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
11. the malaysian is the person who's sport is surfing##1
12. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
