The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bluemaster, havana, alhambra, blend
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the havana-smoker is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Cigar   | alhambra       | havana      | blend      | dunhill | bluemaster  |

