.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: aprild-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
There are 5 different nationalities: american, brazilian, dutch, egyptian, indonesian
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, april, december, february, january
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the brazilian##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the american and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the american is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is aprild-games##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is aprild-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is aprild-games is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | aprild-games |
| Nationality   | american   | egyptian    | brazilian | indonesian | dutch      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| Birthday     | december | january        | march  | april        | february    |

